### Microsoft Graph flow for the provided SharePoint folder link.
### 1. Acquire a delegated token with Sites.Read.All.
### 2. Resolve the site by path.
### 3. List the site drives and match "Documentos Partilhados".
### 4. Enumerate the folder and download files.

@graphHost = https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0
@tenantId = organizations
@siteHost = awareness.sharepoint.com
@sitePath = sites/AW-Autom
@driveId = REPLACE_WITH_DRIVE_ID
@folderPath = Geral/Matriz/AWA_510231845_AWARENESS_Accounting
@accessToken = REPLACE_WITH_BEARER_TOKEN

### Resolve site
GET {{graphHost}}/sites/{{siteHost}}:/{{sitePath}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List document libraries for the site
GET {{graphHost}}/sites/{{siteHost}},REPLACE_SITE_COLLECTION_ID,REPLACE_WEB_ID/drives?$select=id,name,webUrl
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List the target folder children
GET {{graphHost}}/drives/{{driveId}}/root:/{{folderPath}}:/children?$top=200
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Download one file by item id
GET {{graphHost}}/drives/{{driveId}}/items/REPLACE_WITH_ITEM_ID/content
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
